Centered Box Layout with Responsive Design
This project showcases a centered container box with responsive design techniques using Flexbox, Media Queries, and Mobile-First design principles. The design adapts to various screen sizes, providing an optimized experience across devices.

Features
A centered container that adjusts its content dynamically.

Responsive typography and padding for mobile and desktop screens.

Clean design with rounded corners, subtle shadows, and a modern layout.

Technologies Used
HTML - Structure of the page.

CSS - Styling and layout.

Flexbox - For centering elements both vertically and horizontally.

Media Queries - To make the design responsive for various screen sizes.

Mobile-First Approach - Ensures the design is optimized for small screens first